<% layout("/layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h2>Privacy Policy</h2>
    <hr>

    <p>
        Welcome to WanderLust. Your privacy is important to us.
    </p>

    <h4>Information We Collect</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>Name and account information during registration.</li>
        <li>Listings and images uploaded by users.</li>
        <li>Reviews and comments posted on listings.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>How We Use Your Information</h4>
    <ul>
        <li>To provide and improve our services.</li>
        <li>To display your listings and reviews.</li>
        <li>To maintain account security.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Image Storage</h4>
    <p>
        Images uploaded on WanderLust are securely stored using Cloudinary.
    </p>

    <h4>Cookies</h4>
    <p>
        We use session cookies to keep users logged in securely.
    </p>

    <h4>Contact</h4>
    <p>
        For any privacy-related concerns, please contact the WanderLust team.
    </p>
</div>